social_posts.post_text:
Friday Spotlight: Nick Gwiazdowski
Our Takedown athlete pool runs deep, but Gwiz is an OG part of our brand. He is an American freestyle wrestler. A two-time NCAA Division I National Champion and 4x all American for the North Carolina State Wolfpack, Gwiazdowski has won two bronze medals at the World Championships and has captured a Pan American Games title and two Pan American Championships for Team USA. 

Proud to have him on our team and looking forward to him competing in the UWW World Cup in Iowa City next weekend!
It’s beginning to look a lot like Christmas!! Merry Christmas!🌲🎄🎅🏽🤶🏼🧑🏿‍🎄
I hope all my friends had a very Merry Christmas and Happy Hanukkah!  2023 is up next. Get ready.

Breath deep, refocus, and work toward the next points. Cheers. 
📸: @eldonlindsay
